'''Aurora''' ke toropo wa [[Mmušôgaê wa Bergrivier]], [[Mmasepala Setereke tša West Coast]] go feta diprofense [[Kapa Bodikela]] ka moka [[Afrika Borwa]]. Situated 43 km leboa-bohlabela la [[Piketberg]] le 29 km borwa la Redelinghuys. Established in 1906, it was named after the Roman goddess of dawn.

